&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with AE to support the shared book of business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Become a subject matter authority on all CarGurus products (Listings Packages &amp;amp; Digital Suite)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Complete post-sale onboarding for new dealerships and dealership personnel&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be data-driven in quantifying the value of our service to dealers and identifying opportunities for growth and improved results.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Educate dealers on how to maximize the value of the CarGurus platform by leveraging tools, reports, and best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;When appropriate, work with the customer to follow up on technical, billing, and content issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advance cross-departmental collaboration (Support, Billing, Data Integrity, Product, and Engineering) to convey key issues and promote new insights within the CarGurus organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop deep and wide-ranging relationships with dealership decision makers and staff, growing our span of influence and the number of CG Champions within the dealership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
