&lt;li&gt;Perform daily deal activation checks on our closed deals to ensure a seamless customer experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot discrepancies in data between Salesforce and supporting systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with our Inside Sales, Field Sales, and Marketing teams to improve data quality and enrich prospect lists.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
